{{Infobox language |name=Batu |nativename=Afi |region=[[Nigeria]] |speakers=25,000 |date=no date |ref=e08 |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Benue–Congo]] |fam4=[[Southern Bantoid]] |fam5=[[Tivoid languages|Tivoid]] |fam6=North |iso3=btu |glotto=batu1255 |glottorefname=Batu }}
'''Batu''' is a [[Tivoid language]] of [[Nigeria]]. Dialects are Amanda-Afi, Angwe, Kamino.
